<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>selectors</title>
    <style>
        /* universal selector */
        *
        {
           background-color: gray; 
        } 
        /* element selector */
        p
        {
            background-color: green;
        }
        /* class element */
        .object{
            background-color: blueviolet;
        }
        .mypara{
            background-color: brown;
        }
        .span{
            background-color: bisque;
        }
        /* id element */
        #myid{
            background-color: aqua;
            color: blue;
        }
        #css{
            background-color: beige;
            color: greenyellow;
            
        }
        #gg{
            background-color: blue;
            color: blueviolet;
        }
        span{
            background-color: black;
        }
        /* element vth cls selector */
        p.mypara{
            background-color: rgb(153, 226, 43);
        }
        /* element vth id selector */
        h1#myid{
            background-color: rgb(226, 26, 190);
        }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="object">
     
      <h1 id="myid">heading</h1>
      <p class="mypara">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fuga
        aspernatur ratione consequatur exercitationem ullam repellendus
        repudiandae facere sint cupiditate! Ex doloribus, eveniet debitis cum
        temporibus dicta provident delectus est quisquam!
      </p>
      <span class="span" id="gg">this is span</span>
      <div>
        <h2 id="css">second heading</h2>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorem,
          dolores quasi? Repudiandae illum ducimus similique voluptatem, quae,
          asperiores blanditiis perferendis dolorem ad aut recusandae quasi
          distinctio consequuntur, molestias sapiente fuga?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
